MessageQueueConnector
=====================

Helper code to connect to AMQP servers using configurable connection settings.
Specify connection parameters in the config/amqp.yml file

All calls MUST be run inside EventMachine 'reactor' code, due to the nature of 
AMQP driver library that this plugin uses.

Example
=======

EM.run {
  MessageQueue.connect do |channel|
    # stuff
  end
  EM.add_timer(1) { EM.stop_event_loop }
}


